title: United Kingdom Imports of Plastics & Plastic Products
description: Imports of Plastics & Plastic Products in the United Kingdom decreased to 1495.20 GBP Million in September from 1506.91 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Plastics & Plastic Products in the United Kingdom averaged 899.01 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 1667.65 GBP Million in May of 2022 and a record low of 396.17 GBP Million in December of 2001. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Plastics & Plastic Products.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
